=Dragon Warrior (NES) Graphics Data=

This page documents the graphics system, tile organization, and palette structure for Dragon Warrior (NES).

==CHR ROM Organization==

Dragon Warrior uses 16KB of CHR ROM (2 banks of 8KB each) for all graphics data.

